// -----------+------+------------+--------------------------------+------------
// #10/D10    |  PB2 | #15        |  Slave Select			  (SS) | Purple
// #11/D11    |  PB3 | #14        |  Master Out Slave In	(MOSI) | Grey
// #12/D12    |  PB4 | #13        |  Master In Slave Out	(MISO) | Brown
// #13/D13    |  PB5 | #12        |  Clock					 (SCK) | Yellow
// -----------+------+------------+--------------------------+------------
//============================================================================

